# Default dev proxy: `/api` → cloud Node (Render). Matches production / Vercel `BACKEND_BASE`.
# Run only the Vite app: `npm run dev` from repo root — no local server required.
#
# Full local stack instead: create `.env.development.local` (gitignored) with:
#   VITE_API_PROXY=http://127.0.0.1:8080
#   VITE_RECIPE_PROXY=http://127.0.0.1:8080
# then `npm run dev:local` or run `npm run dev:server` in another terminal.
VITE_API_PROXY=https://fit5120-climatequest.onrender.com
VITE_RECIPE_PROXY=https://fit5120-climatequest.onrender.com
